CatDescriptText: George Barbour was an editor of the Pittsburgh Courier.The other time cards include: Ralph Koger, Harvey Wilson, Eirc Roberts, George Pitts, Phyllis Garland, Robert Frye, Phillip Taylor, Beatrice Robinson, Revella Hobson, Frances Williams, Ida Anderson, and Doris Gobble.
TitMainTitle: Pittsburgh Courier staff time clock with three baseballs on top, and time card slots on the side, first card reads, "Pay Ending 4-29-61, Barbour, George"
